data.description: A unique and lovely 3-bedroom, 3-bath ranch-style home in the desirable Westpark subdivision offers a delightful living experience with its spacious living rooms with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. There is a versatile lower level that has been thoughtfully designed and finished to provide additional living space, and a lovely composite deck to enjoy the surrounding natural beauty. It's a wonderful place to create lasting memories and call your home. Message me for a private walk thru. This beauty will not last long in the market, that's for sure! (Owner's have a VA assumable loan)
